    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/bdcd45ae3f329a4f2199fe320bf5a7b4.poster.avif?t=1734430552\" width=800 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/bdcd45ae3f329a4f2199fe320bf5a7b4.webm?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/bdcd45ae3f329a4f2199fe320bf5a7b4.mp4?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注我们了解《洪荒西行录》的最新情报</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进游10大福利礼包大放送（领取方式：角色达到25级-主页-天天返利-兑换码）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYVIP8881</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYVIP9992</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL1113</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL2224</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL3335</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL4446</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL5557</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL6668</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL7779</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HJYXFL8880</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加官方QQ群：729877938，还有更多福利等你来领！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加时请备注：洪荒西行录</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【游戏背景】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上古传说，女娲在天外天建太幽墟，将上古凶兽和血海魔物用神石封印，上古旧神退场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不想千万年后，天帝为了稳固权力，成为真正的天帝之主，用了数千年时间使太幽墟封印松动，同时又忌惮修成圆满的斗战佛孙悟空的神力，便诓骗其舍去佛身重化神石，然而已有诸多魔物挣脱牢笼，祸乱众生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的故事从这里开始，世界是否迎来破晓将由你谱写......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【实景展示】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏打击畅快淋漓，各职业技能炫酷，还原西游原汁原味的经典场景：花果山、盘丝洞、火焰山、凌霄殿、瑶池等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妖猴职业瑶池打斗实录</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/a8653ae0e789ac6058424dcdf713c03a.poster.avif?t=1734430552\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/a8653ae0e789ac6058424dcdf713c03a.webm?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/a8653ae0e789ac6058424dcdf713c03a.mp4?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骨姬职业BOSS打斗实录</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/474e9807d8653fd11e792ba0fdbd8150.poster.avif?t=1734430552\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/474e9807d8653fd11e792ba0fdbd8150.webm?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/474e9807d8653fd11e792ba0fdbd8150.mp4?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵童职业花果山打斗实录</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/def62761c57027e571d720178bee11e7.poster.avif?t=1734430552\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/def62761c57027e571d720178bee11e7.webm?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/def62761c57027e571d720178bee11e7.mp4?t=1734430552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【游戏特色】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★妖魔集结 多职业自由切换</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莲花太子灵童，高爆发战场奇袭；半面狂暴半面佛妖猴，单体PK无人能敌；还有一心修仙的真人和冰肌冷艳的骨姬职业，领略不一样的养成体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/2de0c964272780bcbe8ecbc70a2e6fb2.avif?t=1734430552\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras_big/2de0c964272780bcbe8ecbc70a2e6fb2.avif?t=1734430552 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★超高爆率 顶级装备全掉落</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >割草刷怪收割，宝箱全屏掉落；装备拍卖有保值，惊喜套装飚战力！时尚外观不重样，自由搭配耀全身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/d5495df9d4642ae1a75637d712193ba8.avif?t=1734430552\" width=800 height=440 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★神魔图鉴 诸神万妖全搜罗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡片收集，隐藏属性加不停；封神榜系统的开启，不仅满足你的收集欲，还大大提升了人物属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/151795b3b890469842facc597a2468b8.avif?t=1734430552\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras_big/151795b3b890469842facc597a2468b8.avif?t=1734430552 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★神龙变身 多形态进化养成</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孵蛋、化形、成人、魔化，半神半魔由你选择自由变身！快来探索神龙的终极形态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras/b88b1a83de155d6a968265683a292d81.avif?t=1734430552\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157850/extras_big/b88b1a83de155d6a968265683a292d81.avif?t=1734430552 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通往西行之路已经开启，快跟猴哥一起激斗神魔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
